data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful, 3 story, classic brick colonial situated on a corner lot.  The large covered front porch welcomes you home after a long day.  Inside, the open feel is enhanced by the hardwood floors that flow throughout.  The living room is warm and inviting with large windows that cascade natural light and a cozy fireplace.  Off the kitchen, is a spacious room that can be used as a pantry or appliance storage.  Rounding out the main level are a separate dining area and an office / study.  Up the wood staircase to the second level, you will find 3 nice sized bedrooms, 2 with walk-in closets. As well as a large full bath.  Also you will find access to the third story, this space can be used as a bedroom, rec room or office space.  Completing this home, the full basement is partially finished with the second full bath.  The backyard is fenced, and accesses the detached garage.
